 vary widely from dealer to dealer, though in general, loans from dealerships have higher rates than those you get from banks or credit unions. Recently, regulations that restricted the amount a dealer could mark-up the interest rate on a loan have been pulled back.","Dealerships tend to have less strict credit restrictions than other lenders, so if your credit is poor, CarsDirect may be worth looking into. Be advised that a combination of borrowing through a dealership and low credit can leave you with a very high interest rate. Dealerships also have more flexibility when negotiating, so if you have a large down payment and good credit, you could get a good deal.","CarsDirect offers some advantages compared to banks and credit unions. For example, some lenders have restrictions on the age or mileage of the cars you can buy, but you can get financing for any car you want through CarsDirect, as long as a nearby dealer has it in stock."]},"id":"4d8ee8c8-c469-4cac-81af-20c1714987f7","type":"text"}]],"body":null,"legacyId":"product_review_page_55710","url":"/carsdirect-review","authors":[{"email":"","slug":"eli-mccormick","url":"/author/eli-mccormick","dateCreated":"2019-04-17T20:46:58Z","name":"Eli McCormick","dateModified":"2019-04-17T20:46:58Z","id":"CSoTtbWogSTgZ9Xgr3Anr9","dateImported":null,"site":"toptenreviews"}],"territories":["US","GB"],"companies":[],"dateCreated":"2013-01-22T13:31:46Z","datePublished":"2013-01-22T13:31:46Z","name":"CarsDirect","synopsis":"CarsDirect has tools to help you find cars and auto loans from local dealerships.","review":{"rating":76,"verdict":"CarsDirect has good tools for finding cars nearby, but you only receive loan offers from participating dealerships.","pros":["There are no restrictions on the type of car you can buy."],"cons":["The loan offers come from dealerships only."]},"strapline":"CarsDirect has tools to help you find cars and auto loans from local dealerships.","language":"en","dateModified":"2018-09-14T00:00:00Z","id"